OL,4,Cafter murder as report calls for
OL,5,Coverhaul
OL,7,FToday marks three years since the
OL,8,Fmurder of Sarah Everard in the same
OL,9,Fweek a damning report found a "radical
OL,10,Foverhaul" of policing practices and
OL,11,Fculture is needed.
OL,13,FThe 33-year-old marketing executive
OL,14,Fwas raped and killed by Metropolitan
OL,15,FPolice officer Wayne Couzens, who was
OL,16,Foff duty, as she walked home in south
OL,17,FLondon on March 3, 2021.
