OL,4,Cafter murder as report calls for
OL,5,Coverhaul
OL,7,FThe 51-year-old used his status as a
OL,8,Fpolice officer to trick Ms Everard
OL,9,Finto thinking he could arrest her for
OL,10,Fbreaking lockdown rules in place at
OL,11,Fthe time.
OL,13,FMs Everard's family said she died
OL,14,Fbecause Couzens was a police officer
OL,15,Fand she "would never have got into a
OL,16,Fstranger's car".
OL,18,FCouzens should never have been given a
OL,19,Fjob as a police officer and chances to
OL,20,Fstop the sexual predator were
OL,21,Frepeatedly ignored and missed.
