OL,7,FSeveral women's rights organisations
OL,8,Fand charities have taken to social
OL,9,Fmedia to share tributes to Ms Everard.
OL,11,FA statement from Solace Women's Aid
OL,12,Fcondemned the lack of action, reading:
OL,13,F"Our deep sadness at what happened to
OL,14,FSarah three years ago has not changed.
OL,16,F"Once again, we send our thoughts and
OL,17,Four love to her family and her
OL,18,Ffriends, and to so many other women
OL,19,Fwho have been through too much trauma
OL,20,Fand abuse over the last few decades.
