OL,7,FMarking the anniversary, the Mayor of
OL,8,FLondon Sadiq Khan said his thoughts
OL,9,Fare with the family and loved ones of
OL,10,FMs Everard on the "unimaginably
OL,11,Fdifficult day" which marks the third
OL,12,Fanniversary of her murder.
OL,14,FMr Khan said it will "take years" to
OL,15,Frepair the damaged trust and
OL,16,Fconfidence in the police.
