OL,7,F"My thoughts are with the family and
OL,8,Floved ones of Sarah Everard on the
OL,9,Fthird anniversary of her tragic death,
OL,10,Fon what must be an unimaginably
OL,11,Fdifficult day for all those who knew
OL,12,Fand loved Sarah," he said.
OL,14,F"Sarah's murder by a serving police
OL,15,Fofficer horrified the entire country
OL,16,Fand significantly damaged the trust
OL,17,Fand confidence women and girls have in
OL,18,Fthe police. This will take years to
OL,19,Frepair."
