OL,7,FMs Everard's abduction and murder
OL,8,Fgalvanised demands for tackling
OL,9,Fviolence towards women.
OL,11,FMr Khan said: "We owe it to Sarah,
OL,12,FZara Aleena, Sabina Nessa, Nicole
OL,13,FSmallman, Bibaa Henry and every other
OL,14,Fwoman who has had their life brutally
OL,15,Fstolen from them to do all we can to
OL,16,Fprevent violence against women and
