OL,7,FIn March 2023, the Casey Review,
OL,8,Fcommissioned by the Met in the wake of
OL,9,FMs Everard's murder, found the force
OL,10,Fwas institutionally racist, homophobic
OL,11,Fand misogynist, and there might be
OL,12,Fmore officers like Couzens in its
OL,13,Franks.
OL,15,F"As mayor, I have ensured the Met is
OL,16,Fnow on a path of far-reaching reform
OL,17,Fand we are starting to see some
OL,18,Fimprovements, with stronger vetting
OL,19,Fand the removal of more rogue police
OL,20,Fofficers and staff," Mr Khan said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU|D@TO]
