OL,7,F"But the recent findings from the
OL,8,FAngiolini Inquiry highlight how far
OL,9,Fpolicing in this country still has to
OL,10,Fgo to raise standards and rebuild
OL,11,Ftrust.
OL,13,F"I will continue to do everything in
OL,14,Fmy power to support and hold the
OL,15,FCommissioner to account on delivering
OL,16,Fthe vital cultural and performance
OL,17,Freforms needed so that we can continue
OL,18,Fbuilding a safer London for everyone `
OL,19,Fparticularly for women and girls who
OL,20,Fhave been let down for far too long."
