OL,7,FLaw graduate, Zara Aleena, 35, was
OL,8,Fmurdered by Jordan McSweeney as she
OL,9,Fwalked home from a night out in
OL,10,FIlford, east London, on June 26, 2022.
OL,12,FHer killer was jailed for life but a
OL,13,Fprobation report in January found
OL,14,FMcSweeney had been incorrectly
OL,15,Fassessed as medium rather than high
OL,16,Frisk when he was freed from his ninth
OL,17,Fprison term.
OL,19,FThis meant he should have been
OL,20,Freturned to jail for breaching the
OL,21,Fterms of his release.
