OL,7,FSabina Nessa, a 28-year-old primary
OL,8,Fschool teacher, was murdered by
OL,9,FAlbanian-born Koci Selamaj in south-
OL,10,Feast London on September 17, 2021.
OL,12,FAfter her murder, Mr Khan said there
OL,13,Fwas "an epidemic" of violence against
OL,14,Fwomen and girls.
OL,16,FSisters Nicole Smallman, 27, and Bibaa
OL,17,FHenry, 46, were stabbed to death by
OL,18,FDanyal Hussein in north-west London on
OL,19,FJune 6, 2020.
